	<Title>
		Sports drinks: Better than water?
	</Title>
	<Body>
		&lt;p&gt;Water is generally the best way to replace lost fluids. But if you&apos;re exercising for more than 60 minutes, use a sports drink. Sports drinks can help maintain your body&apos;s electrolyte balance and give you a bit more energy because they contain carbohydrates.&lt;/p&gt;
